Responsibilities:
Manage and grow the Analytical business in Jurong Island Cluster.
To achieve/exceed bookings, sales and profitability targets set for Analytical business in Jurong Island.
Plan and implement promotional seminars for new and existing customers.
Work with Sales Support team for order processing and service team to ensure service requests are met.
Pursuit wireless opportunities in Jurong Island Cluster.
Responsible for service sales and spare parts revenue in both MRO & Project Business, including maintenance contract for install base in Jurong Island.
Requirements:
Diploma/Degree in Engineering with 1 to 3 years’ relevant sales experience in the process industry.
Good analytical and questioning skills coupled with ability to develop and implement sales strategies.
Strong in interpersonal and communication skills, especially influencing skills.